Text:
Hmm, it doesn't work for me. When I try to run the setup-file in the Polish UI-folder, it says "this patch isn't meant for your version of the program", or something like that.
And the program doesn't accept the key generated by the keygen; says it's taken by another computer. Reading lipa4r's instructions I assume it won't work until I've run both the polish setups correctly. Anyone experienced the same problem?

Ah, I got it. Choose to activate over phone, then you get an installation-ID (different from the serial) that you are supposed to give to the Abbyy-people. Feed the keygen with THAT code, not with the serial.
run setup, enter code in serial.txt, run application, chose activation via phone, enter code generated by keygen. bachka!
